# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Personal session artifacts — stay local, not shared with framework users
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# User journal (per-session narrative — each framework user keeps their own)
docs/current-state.md
tasks/handoff.md
tasks/session-log.md
tasks/session-log-*.md

# Personal project decisions (architectural decisions go in tasks/decisions.md)
tasks/decisions-personal.md

# All per-topic in-flight work artifacts under tasks/
# (proposals, challenges, judgments, refines, plans, findings, designs,
#  reviews, explores, thinks, debates, polishes, QAs, analyses,
#  investigations, validations, specs, flows, premortems, audits,
#  benchmarks, variance studies, critiques, ground-truths, adjudications,
#  arm outputs, coverage, mappings, anonymization summaries, etc.)
# Only the curated governance files stay in git (whitelist below).
tasks/*.md
tasks/*.json
tasks/*/
tasks/_archive/

# Keep curated framework governance
!tasks/README.md
!tasks/decisions.md
!tasks/lessons.md
!tasks/lessons-archived.md
!tasks/handoff.md.template
!tasks/session-log.md.template
!docs/current-state.md.template
